(370, 2, '2015-10-22 04:04:43', '2015-10-22 04:04:43', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="100px"][vc_custom_heading source="post_title" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p>SpeedonX is the 1st online platform for Bikers in Bangladesh established in 2018. SpeedonX comes with a platform for riders! The company is registered as SpeedonX Private Limited.</p>\r\n<p>Bangladesh is a fast moving country, having advancement in every sector. We wish to contribute to this Riding Generation by giving the best facilities to move fast, reach new boundaries and achieve new heights. We believe, your greatest opportunities are those you havent yet explored.</p>\r\n<p>You could have the desire for an elegant body, or you need a fuel-efficient engine, could be the break discs, or could be a scooter for your day to day activities, or could just be a dead fast engine that you crave, we have all your bikes in one single platform. We are committed to provide you the best that you deserve and you dream of, right at your fingertips.</p>\r\n<p>Our services are not only limited to providing your desired bikes, we are also committed in providing you the best deals that you could possibly want for your bikes. You will get the best deals with the best value-added services for your motorbikes.</p>\r\n<p>We represent one single platform for the leading motorcycle brands in Bangladesh together. We are dedicated in offering you what you need for your motorbikes, ranging from registered service centers, lubricants, insurance policy packages and other lucrative deals all together in one platform.</p>\r\n<p>We are welcoming all the Bike Lovers to our beloved online platform  SpeedonX.</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2019-07-28 14:14:14', '2019-07-28 14:14:14', '', 0, 'http://bikes.